		<h1 class="headings shadow">User Experience</h1>
		<p class="p-justified">I look at every line of code I write imagining myself as a first time user. I contemplate if the interface is intuitive, pleasant to experience, and if it draws me to return. My focus to optimize the user experience is page load speed, caching data, preloading, or if preloading isn’t possible, distracting the user with something they like. In some cases, that could be a floating tennis ball.</p>		
	</div>
