		<h1 class="headings shadow p-right">DRY Code</h1>
		<p class="p-justified">Taking the ring to Mordor and breakfast doesn’t always need to be two separate functions. I strive to use code efficiently. Sometimes that may be an object literal collecting similar methods or a donut Class calling on an Elvish module that might just be used for a Prophecy.prototype object in a different controller.</p>		
	</div>
