		<h1 class="headings shadow p-right">Getting Help</h1>
		<p class="p-justified">We all find ourselves in code that is a bit beyond our abilities to intuit our way through. Every coder knows how to find answers, but the real skill is in finding the path of least resistance to your understanding in every new situation. Should I jump down the rabbit hole of Stack Overflow, or interrupt my coworker across the room? Sometimes it’s a combination of both. Become as familiar as you can using your impersonal resources so that when you talk to a person, you don’t take much of their time.</p>		
